<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.3">
<l>vitiyiṉāl peṭaimaṇakku meṉṉaṭaiya vaṉṉaṅkāṇ</l>
<l>matiyiṉāl kuṟaṇmāṇā yulakiranta kaḷvarkku</l>
<l>matiyilēṉ valviṉaiyē māḷātō veṉṟorutti</l>
<l>matiyellā muḷkalaṅki mayaṅkumā leṉṉīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Soft-gaited geese who unite with [your] females by fate,</l>
<l>speak</l>
<l>to the robber who begged for the earth as a glory of a dwarf, by [his] mind:</l>
	<l>“a woman is confused, all [her] mind stirred up inside,</l>
<l>saying ‘won’t the harsh deeds of me without mind be exhausted’.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
